# Environment variables

Copy to `.env` at repo root and `services/api/.env`.

```bash
# ─── Cognee Cloud (mobile + optional remote sync) ───
COGNEE_API_KEY=
COGNEE_BASE_URL=https://api.cognee.ai

# ─── Speechmatics (mobile voice STT) ───
SPEECHMATICS_API_KEY=
SPEECHMATICS_REGION=eu

# ─── Cognee (local) ───
COGNEE_DATA_PATH=./data/cognee
COGNEE_DB=kuzu
COGNEE_DATASET_PREFIX=dear-diary
# Required for cognify/graph extraction (OpenAI, Groq, etc.)
LLM_API_KEY=
# Disable multi-tenant auth for local hackathon demo
ENABLE_BACKEND_ACCESS_CONTROL=false

# ─── API sidecar ───
API_HOST=127.0.0.1
API_PORT=8787
API_VERSION=0.1.0

# ─── Gradium ───
GRADIUM_API_KEY=
GRADIUM_VOICE_ID=
# Coupon if needed: RAISE-2026

# ─── Gemma @ Crusoe ───
CRUSOE_API_KEY=
CRUSOE_BASE_URL=
CRUSOE_MODEL=gemma-4-31b-it

# ─── Fallback LLM (optional) ───
VULTR_INFERENCE_KEY=
USE_VULTR_FALLBACK=0

# ─── Desktop (Vite) ───
VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
VITE_USE_MSW=true

# ─── Feature flags ───
FEATURE_CONNECTORS=0
FEATURE_VOICE_CLONE=0
FEATURE_IMPROVE=1

# ─── Demo ───
SEED_PROFILE=maya-30d
```

## Never commit

- `.env`
- `services/api/data/`
- API keys
